<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="145" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="145">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="145">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="145">Male.</emphasis>
Clypeus dorsally elevated, sloping ventrally. Mandible with sharp subapical and large inner subbasal teeth (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 13–18" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 13 - 18. Arkaditilla spp., ♂, face 13 A. bagrada (Cameron) 14 A. depressicornis (Mickel) 15 A. frim sp. nov., holotype 16 A. gibba sp. nov., paratype 17 A. leleji sp. nov., holotype 18 A. nallinia (Zavattari)." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.84.68709.figures13-18" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/579482" pageId="0" pageNumber="145">18</figureCitation>
), ventrally deeply excised with large basal tooth (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 19–36" captionStartId="F4" captionText="Figures 19 - 36. Arkaditilla spp., ♂ 19 - 24 mandible, lateral view 25, 27, 29, 31, 33, 35 scape, ventral view 26, 28, 30, 32, 34, 36 pedicel, F 1, and F 2, lateral view 19, 25, 26 A. bagrada (Cameron) 20, 27, 28 A. depressicornis (Mickel) 21, 29, 30 A. frim sp. nov., holotype 22, 31, 32 A. gibba sp. nov., holotype 23, 33, 34 A. leleji sp. nov., holotype 24, 35, 36 A. nallinia (Zavattari)." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.84.68709.figures19-36" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/579483" pageId="0" pageNumber="145">24</figureCitation>
). Scape ventral carinae divergent apically (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 19–36" captionStartId="F4" captionText="Figures 19 - 36. Arkaditilla spp., ♂ 19 - 24 mandible, lateral view 25, 27, 29, 31, 33, 35 scape, ventral view 26, 28, 30, 32, 34, 36 pedicel, F 1, and F 2, lateral view 19, 25, 26 A. bagrada (Cameron) 20, 27, 28 A. depressicornis (Mickel) 21, 29, 30 A. frim sp. nov., holotype 22, 31, 32 A. gibba sp. nov., holotype 23, 33, 34 A. leleji sp. nov., holotype 24, 35, 36 A. nallinia (Zavattari)." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.84.68709.figures19-36" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/579483" pageId="0" pageNumber="145">35</figureCitation>
), densely punctate between them; F1 apical 1/3, F2 and F3 basal 1/3 whitish yellow on ventral half; F1 strongly depressed, F1 height ~0.8
<normalizedToken originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
pedicel diameter (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 19–36" captionStartId="F4" captionText="Figures 19 - 36. Arkaditilla spp., ♂ 19 - 24 mandible, lateral view 25, 27, 29, 31, 33, 35 scape, ventral view 26, 28, 30, 32, 34, 36 pedicel, F 1, and F 2, lateral view 19, 25, 26 A. bagrada (Cameron) 20, 27, 28 A. depressicornis (Mickel) 21, 29, 30 A. frim sp. nov., holotype 22, 31, 32 A. gibba sp. nov., holotype 23, 33, 34 A. leleji sp. nov., holotype 24, 35, 36 A. nallinia (Zavattari)." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.84.68709.figures19-36" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/579483" pageId="0" pageNumber="145">36</figureCitation>
). T3 orange (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 7–12" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 7 - 12. Arkaditilla spp., ♂, habitus 7, 9, 11 dorsal view 8, 10, 12 lateral view 7, 8 A. gibba sp. nov., holotype 9, 10 A. leleji sp. nov., holotype 11, 12 A. nallinia (Zavattari). Scale bars: 3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.84.68709.figures7-12" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/579481" pageId="0" pageNumber="145">12</figureCitation>
); cuspis strongly widened on posterior 1/3 with rounded apex (Figs 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 49–66" captionStartId="F6" captionText="Figures 49 - 66. Arkaditilla spp., ♂, genitalia 49, 52, 55, 58, 61, 64 genital capsule and volsella, inner view 50, 53, 56, 59, 62, 65 left penis valve 51, 54, 57, 60, 63, 66 right penis valve 49 - 51 A. bagrada (Cameron) 52 - 54 A. depressicornis (Mickel) 55 - 57 A. frim sp. nov., holotype 58 - 60 A. gibba sp. nov., holotype 61 - 63 A. leleji sp. nov., holotype 64 - 66 A. nallinia (Zavattari)." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.84.68709.figures49-66" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/579485" pageId="0" pageNumber="145">64</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 67–72" captionStartId="F7" captionText="Figures 67 - 72. Arkaditilla spp., ♂, genital volsella, ventro-inner view 67 A. bagrada (Cameron) 68 A. depressicornis (Mickel) 69 A. frim sp. nov., holotype 70 A. gibba sp. nov., holotype 71 A. leleji sp. nov., holotype 72 A. nallinia (Zavattari). White arrows indicate the paracuspis." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.84.68709.figures67-72" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/579486" pageId="0" pageNumber="145">72</figureCitation>
); digitus posteriorly expanded, forming triangular projection (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 37–48" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figures 37 - 48. Arkaditilla spp., ♂, genitalia 37, 39, 41, 43, 45, 47 dorsal view 38, 40, 42, 44, 46, 48 ventral view 37, 38 A. bagrada (Cameron) 39, 40 A. depressicornis (Mickel) 41, 42 A. frim sp. nov., holotype 43, 44 A. gibba sp. nov., holotype 45, 46 A. leleji sp. nov., holotype 47, 48 A. nallinia (Zavattari)." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.84.68709.figures37-48" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/579484" pageId="0" pageNumber="145">47</figureCitation>
); paracuspis slightly tuberculate (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 67–72" captionStartId="F7" captionText="Figures 67 - 72. Arkaditilla spp., ♂, genital volsella, ventro-inner view 67 A. bagrada (Cameron) 68 A. depressicornis (Mickel) 69 A. frim sp. nov., holotype 70 A. gibba sp. nov., holotype 71 A. leleji sp. nov., holotype 72 A. nallinia (Zavattari). White arrows indicate the paracuspis." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.84.68709.figures67-72" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/579486" pageId="0" pageNumber="145">72</figureCitation>
); penis valve weakly expanded ventrally (Figs 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 49–66" captionStartId="F6" captionText="Figures 49 - 66. Arkaditilla spp., ♂, genitalia 49, 52, 55, 58, 61, 64 genital capsule and volsella, inner view 50, 53, 56, 59, 62, 65 left penis valve 51, 54, 57, 60, 63, 66 right penis valve 49 - 51 A. bagrada (Cameron) 52 - 54 A. depressicornis (Mickel) 55 - 57 A. frim sp. nov., holotype 58 - 60 A. gibba sp. nov., holotype 61 - 63 A. leleji sp. nov., holotype 64 - 66 A. nallinia (Zavattari)." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.84.68709.figures49-66" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/579485" pageId="0" pageNumber="145">65</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 49–66" captionStartId="F6" captionText="Figures 49 - 66. Arkaditilla spp., ♂, genitalia 49, 52, 55, 58, 61, 64 genital capsule and volsella, inner view 50, 53, 56, 59, 62, 65 left penis valve 51, 54, 57, 60, 63, 66 right penis valve 49 - 51 A. bagrada (Cameron) 52 - 54 A. depressicornis (Mickel) 55 - 57 A. frim sp. nov., holotype 58 - 60 A. gibba sp. nov., holotype 61 - 63 A. leleji sp. nov., holotype 64 - 66 A. nallinia (Zavattari)." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.84.68709.figures49-66" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/579485" pageId="0" pageNumber="145">66</figureCitation>
). 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="145">Female.</emphasis>
Unknown.
</paragraph>
